{"id":"ce2db86aaf6ab0d5da72b8bdfdaeaa19213a2cd4003aed1a1a6006d1de3607bb","item_id":"af31e56b05:0","text":"在 Blender 中使用 UDIM 非常直接。"}
{"id":"f73a329ff03bd1833222c21656da88deebe1718efedf68cc427a32e45f710ff1","item_id":"af31e56b05:1","text":"如果你的纹理使用 Mari UDIM 样式，且文件名为："}
{"id":"f6ddd0fabef4f6d8daf8b2146cd2954cd3e7bd099b38839d4a9ce8619e9cc24e","item_id":"af31e56b05:2","text":"Diffuse.1001.tex"}
{"id":"f6ddd0fabef4f6d8daf8b2146cd2954cd3e7bd099b38839d4a9ce8619e9cc24e","item_id":"af31e56b05:17","text":"Diffuse.1001.tex"}
{"id":"3d8a8402b9f7b54bae6f5aa37074b1b3cb8173b12a6d70c1d25472d01d78a815","item_id":"af31e56b05:3","text":"，则需要将"}
{"id":"e5e1e2b3b2ea6e5e3e3294eb36b6d7ff4a7cc8fb79e891e166361284569defa7","item_id":"af31e56b05:4","text":"Atlas Style（图集样式）"}
{"id":"e5e1e2b3b2ea6e5e3e3294eb36b6d7ff4a7cc8fb79e891e166361284569defa7","item_id":"af31e56b05:14","text":"Atlas Style（图集样式）"}
{"id":"dd2c2b24cafe4ce4ff075da61675acfd2166b9329868109331ef75fde16f3ffa","item_id":"af31e56b05:5","text":"设置为 UDIM (Mari)，并在 Filename（文件名）参数中使用"}
{"id":"5766853952bff5d739e8d333beedbd24f339ea2c38077a6611da90ca2bcacbd4","item_id":"af31e56b05:6","text":"Diffuse.<UDIM>.tex"}
{"id":"5766853952bff5d739e8d333beedbd24f339ea2c38077a6611da90ca2bcacbd4","item_id":"af31e56b05:19","text":"Diffuse.<UDIM>.tex"}
{"id":"c21f9ccabe69b75f65093e33c3c9d8a4fbc1e3821d8ea91c7489b58ac4792164","item_id":"af31e56b05:7","text":"这样纹理才能加载到正确的 UDIM 中。"}
{"id":"303c71975870f191f23863869bcf645ac30c425858d1feba5d3dadbea26d8dd2","item_id":"af31e56b05:8","text":"注意：<UDIM> 可以使用大写，也可以使用小写 <udim>。"}
{"id":"bceeacc668934bc699c0f230b3809c91365c843556470744ce4bec190e59f864","item_id":"af31e56b05:9","text":"第一个 UV tile 的 Mari UDIM 示例为"}
{"id":"f6ddd0fabef4f6d8daf8b2146cd2954cd3e7bd099b38839d4a9ce8619e9cc24e","item_id":"af31e56b05:10","text":"Diffuse.1001.tex"}
{"id":"76f0227cadc9d1c75b897f233f204a0fceeb97b05508273726ea30bf75017a24","item_id":"af31e56b05:11","text":"其中 \"1001\" 会替换纹理文件名中的 <UDIM>。"}
{"id":"8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e","item_id":"af31e56b05:12","text":"Value（值）"}
{"id":"971b974235a86ca628dcc713d6e2e8d975206cc84c858720ce046c2dab72855a","item_id":"af31e56b05:13","text":"Filename（文件名）"}
{"id":"1cac5ea5460e7817a8242aee809f78e4212886802c123875cfebd09b92fd3b72","item_id":"af31e56b05:15","text":"Use in path（路径中使用）"}
